+/**
+ * JavaSteam's auth methods (`pollAuthSessionStatus`, `sendSteamGuardCode`, …)
+ * are built with kotlinx-coroutines' `future{}` builder and documented as
+ * `@Throws(AuthenticationException::class)`. But `Future.get()` always wraps
